 {"id":"franken_numpy-rco","title":"Add hfft/ihfft Hermitian FFT functions","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-03-22T02:23:39.183769024Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-22T02:36:58.648987748Z","closed_at":"2026-03-22T02:36:58.648316136Z","close_reason":"Implemented hfft() and ihfft() Hermitian FFT functions. hfft computes irfft(conj(input))*n (unnormalized), ihfft computes conj(rfft(input))/n. Added 3 tests. Note: can't run tests due to pre-existing BinaryOp compile errors from another agent.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
 {"id":"franken_numpy-rd0","title":"Implement iinfo/finfo type information + binary_repr/base_repr base conversion","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-03-22T17:37:10.633368991Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-22T17:40:28.699483009Z","closed_at":"2026-03-22T17:40:28.698823170Z","close_reason":"Implemented 4 remaining NumPy functions: iinfo(dtype) returns (bits, min, max), finfo(dtype) returns (bits, eps, min_positive, max), binary_repr(num, width) for two's complement binary strings, base_repr(number, base, padding) for base-N conversion. 12 tests. Only np.frompyfunc remains excluded (requires Python FFI).","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
